{"tid":787970,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"學校舉辦手淫比賽 校長報警處理","createTime":"2018-08-21T06:02:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T14:45:25.000Z","uid":1426,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"63720240fc817acb856d38fef9e0508faf326aea","tid":787970,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T06:02:49.000Z","msg":"9 t+ H% Z: f1 Q2 }5 ~<br />\n檳島浮羅山背某中學將於8月19日下午2時在學校舉辦「手淫比賽」？有關校方鄭重否認該校會舉辦這項比賽，並報警處理8 V% o: \\7 v( L&quot; ^<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n該校學生事務副校長是於7月31日晚上接獲學校書記的詢問，才知道有網友在面子書流傳消息，指該校將於8月19日舉辦該「手淫比賽」。<br />\n<br />\n根據該面子書貼文，參賽資格必須刮乾淨私處的毛髮及自備參考刊物（色情刊物等），而舉辦單位將提供肥皂給參賽者。<br />\n  <br />\n西南區警區主任安峇拉甘今日證實此事，並指該校副校長已針對此貼文向警方報案。<br />\n<br />\n來源:<br />\n<a href=\"http://share.itudia.com/masturbation-competition/attachment/1212/8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fshare.itudia.com%2Fmasturbation-competition%2Fattachment%2F1212%2F8&d=ogEaDYtAKoEXuTJTj9L6UgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=ef3a2343\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://share.itudia.com/masturbation-competition/attachment/1212/8</a>"},{"pid":"e494346abfab9a0847aed30a03c15af277787c62","tid":787970,"uid":21819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T06:04:29.000Z","msg":"點為之贏"},{"pid":"10e2719f9ec0b37a177380740344fa5e3b30c125","tid":787970,"uid":46678,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T06:04:40.000Z","msg":"生命麵包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4078d1e676c0441482e8f4a1ad98bef291736187","tid":787970,"uid":12498,"like":6,"dislike":9,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T06:06:36.000Z","msg":"打飛機都要監管，香港已4"},{"pid":"ca28dc2b072013d032c74824785a21b300db6bf6","tid":787970,"uid":88887,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T06:10:04.000Z","msg":"校長係咪唔抵得人地持久過佢"},{"pid":"901af39caeb24f7ab045eb0f329e9cdac2e30610","tid":787970,"uid":170383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T0